<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{object}} – FundingHero</title>
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif; 
      margin:0; 
      padding:20px; 
      background:#f5f5f5; 
      color:#333; 
    }
    .email-container { 
      max-width:400px; 
      margin:0 auto; 
      background:#fff; 
      padding:20px; 
      border-radius:8px; 
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }
    .banner { 
      width:100%; 
      height:auto; 
      border-radius:8px 8px 0 0; 
      margin-bottom:20px; 
    }
    .main-message { 
      font-size:16px; 
      margin-bottom:10px; 
    }
    .title { 
      color:#333; 
      font-size:24px; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      margin-bottom:10px; 
    }
    .challenge-type { 
      color:#333; 
      font-size:16px; 
      margin-bottom:20px; 
      font-weight:bold; 
    }
    .description { 
      color:#666; 
      font-size:14px; 
      line-height:1.4; 
      margin-bottom:20px; 
    }
    .credentials { 
      background:#fff; 
      padding:15px; 
      border-radius:6px; 
      border:2px solid #E6B800; 
      margin-bottom:20px; 
    }
    .credential-item { 
      color:#333; 
      font-size:14px; 
      margin-bottom:8px; 
    }
    .credential-value { 
      color:#B8860B; 
      font-weight:bold; 
    }
    .access-link { 
      color:#333; 
      font-size:14px; 
      line-height:1.5; 
      margin-bottom:20px; 
    }
    .access-link a { 
      color:#E6B800; 
      text-decoration:none; 
    }
    .action-button { 
      background:#E6B800; 
      color:#fff; 
      padding:12px 20px; 
      border:none; 
      border-radius:6px; 
      font-size:16px; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      width:100%; 
      text-align:center; 
      text-decoration:none; 
      display:block; 
      cursor:pointer; 
      box-sizing:border-box; 
      margin-bottom:20px; 
    }
    .action-button:hover { 
      background:#B8860B; 
    }
    .steps { 
      background:#fff; 
      padding:15px; 
      border-radius:6px; 
      border:2px solid #E6B800; 
      margin-bottom:20px; 
    }
    .steps-title { 
      color:#B8860B; 
      font-size:14px; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      margin-bottom:10px; 
    }
    .steps-list { 
      color:#333; 
      font-size:12px; 
      line-height:1.4; 
    }
    .highlight { 
      color:#DAA520; 
      font-weight:bold; 
    }
    .footer-text { 
      color:#666; 
      font-size:12px; 
      text-align:center; 
    }
    .company-name { 
      color:#E6B800; 
      font-weight:bold; 
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="FundingHero Banner" class="banner">

    <div class="main-message">Hola, <strong>{{correo}}</strong></div>
    <div class="title">{{object}}</div>
    <div class="challenge-type">{{challenge_type}} – ${{account_size}}</div>
    <div class="description">You can start trading immediately with your access credentials.</div>

    <div class="access-link">
      Para acceder a la cuenta, <strong>{{login_details.username}}</strong>. Se necesita ingresar a <a href="https://demo.tradelocker.com" target="_blank">https://demo.tradelocker.com/es/trade</a>, usando el correo, la contraseña y el servidor.
    </div>

    <div class="credentials">
      <div class="credential-item"><strong>Correo:</strong> <span class="credential-value">{{correo}}</span></div>
      <div class="credential-item"><strong>Contraseña:</strong> <span class="credential-value">{{login_details.password}}</span></div>
      <div class="credential-item"><strong>Servidor:</strong> <span class="credential-value">{{login_details.server}}</span></div>
      <div class="credential-item"><strong>Login:</strong> <span class="credential-value">{{login_details.username}}</span></div>
    </div>

    <a href="{{landingUrl}}" class="action-button" target="_blank">View Dashboard</a>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="steps-title">Next steps:</div>
      <div class="steps-list">
        1. Connect to {{platform}} with the credentials<br>
        2. Review the challenge rules<br>
        3. Start trading according to your strategy<br>
        4. Monitor your progress on the dashboard
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="description">
      <span class="highlight">Thank you for choosing us!</span>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-text">
      Best regards,<br>
      <span class="company-name">FundingHero</span> Team
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>